{"tid":189480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(反韓)需賠 9000 萬！中國法院判 Samsung 侵犯華為專利","createTime":"2017-04-06T12:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T20:43:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f12ee6c07a18c8f202ae17f4d4d1efe1cf0cb77","tid":189480,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"2017-04-06<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20170405_samsung_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20170405_samsung_01.jpg&h=6b118587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然 S8 尚未正式開賣，但 Samsung 似乎又將面臨一大難題。<br />\n<br />\n近日位於中國福建的泉州中院，正式就華為控告 Samsung 侵權一案作出宣判，判 Samsung 在中國的三間子公司侵犯華為專利成立，須賠償 8000 萬人民幣，換算約港幣 9000 萬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news/20160222_gs7_handson_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews%2F20160222_gs7_handson_01.jpg&h=28e1433c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為控告 Samsung 所推出的 Galaxy S7 edge、S7、J5 以及其他 20 多款平板，侵犯華為於 2011 年所取得的 8 項圖型操作介面專利技術。<br />\n<br />\n據泉州網報導，涉案專利是 GUI 的「框架性核心專利」，可解決「如何使用戶簡便地在多個分頻範圍內移動，擺放特定APP圖標的問題」，並提升介面操作的成功率和準確性。<br />\n<br />\n到底此案成為中國其他專利官司的頭炮呢？我們拭目以待吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=14820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Fnews2.php%3Fid%3D14820&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=48f7c232\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=14820</a>"},{"pid":"2d0ce9d204c6fb0b003db93afd8ed12e9b4a02f0","tid":189480,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"支那邏輯。"},{"pid":"d30286d9c14c0b22e8b7a75ffefc919191fa76f9","tid":189480,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T12:44:47.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0c30abf6eb2918690df5b91fb2ebb84a2ca42a"